WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.000
The month 十二ヶ月 一年十二ヶ月の名称

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:22.000
January, February, March, April, May, June, July, August, September, October, November, December

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:34.000
一年の最初の月は正月ですから 一年の第十二番目の月は十二月ですまで

00:00:52.000 --> 00:01:04.000
The sixth month of the year is June. The seventh month of the year is July. The eighth month of the year is August.

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:15.000
The ninth month of the year is September. The tenth month of the year is October. The eleventh month of the year is November.

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:25.000
The twelfth month of the year is December. The first day of January is called the New Year's Day.

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:37.000
正月の第一日は元日と申します。 The last day of December is called the New Year's Eve.

00:01:37.000 --> 00:01:46.000
十二月の最後の日は序夜と申します。 How many days are there in January?

00:01:46.000 --> 00:01:53.000
正月には幾日ありますか? There are thirty-one days in January.

00:01:53.000 --> 00:02:00.000
正月には三十一日あります。 How many days are there in February?

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:06.000
正月には幾日ありますか? There are twenty-eight days.

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:14.000
二十八日あります。 Once in four years, February has twenty-nine days.

00:02:14.000 --> 00:02:22.000
四年に一度、二月に二十九日あります。 Then it is leap year.

00:02:22.000 --> 00:02:30.000
その時は潤年です。 How many days are there in a year?

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:39.000
一年には幾日ありますか? There are three hundred and sixty-five days.

00:02:39.000 --> 00:02:48.000
一年には三百六十五日あります。 In leap years, we have one day more.

00:02:48.000 --> 00:02:53.000
潤年にはもう一日余計にあります。 In leap years, we have one day more.

00:02:53.000 --> 00:02:59.000
言葉、ことわざ、Make hay while the sun shines.

00:02:59.000 --> 00:03:06.000
日の出る間に草を干せ。 Hunger is the best source.

00:03:06.000 --> 00:03:11.000
空腹は何よりの調味料です。 Hunger is the best seasoning.

